{"tid":1550534,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"多謝左膠","createTime":"2019-09-07T16:27:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T20:39:31.000Z","uid":140022,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"35039059ec9e947b103bd82aed5c328eb02ed50a","tid":1550534,"uid":140022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:27:39.000Z","msg":"又害死哂班手足 多謝曬<br />\n原本諗住左膠都係同路人 唔好打佢地<br />\n下次見到打撚埋你 打得勁撚過班藍<br />\n啲左膠又唔見啲狗同藍絲對我地有暴力果時岀現<br />\n垃圾到不得了"},{"pid":"1a6b891ba3c312ddeacaf2442240a00b4d610173","tid":1550534,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:28:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3f87aba8d8a01ba32e51b4fb9f90f3f689e4b193","tid":1550534,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:32:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02ededc2d2168e7e0270333e2cd9b35f0d912241","tid":1550534,"uid":296445,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:38:05.000Z","msg":"將軍澳班左膠, 屌佢老母叫唔好打仲要阻撚住, 你唔打就走撚開啦"},{"pid":"436e8fe7c0aa078fc52f3aba97413fe4f2f22922","tid":1550534,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T20:23:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">左膠永遠都唔係同路人<br />\n<br />\n荃灣黑夜 要前線放藍衫走<br />\n結果同一班藍衫轉頭斬斷其他手足手筋腳筋攪到個手足殘廢 同有手足比人爆頭<br />\n到今日岩岩機場 逼手足放個用磚頭爆手足頭既藍絲走<br />\n<br />\n重有依2個月好多單左膠死攬傷人者<br />\n根本班撚樣只係為光環 欺善怕惡<br />\n對住黑社會就淆底唔敢阻黑社會斬人<br />\n對住自己手足 知手足唔會打佢地<br />\n就大大力阻手足還拖 同講廢話訓前線話<br />\n話會扣幾多分 會失民意<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"48a8ac81c0554219a390d745e3f45e842b217c21","tid":1550534,"uid":64131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T20:24:27.000Z","msg":"阻止即係同黨啦   打撚埋佢"},{"pid":"08a3f6baae91dcda2e4a30f7af78ae36d27322a8","tid":1550534,"uid":92836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T20:28:52.000Z","msg":"有冇人口政策關注組呀<br />\n<br />\n革命後，香港有普選咁又點？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1551006\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1551006</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2acea4e55969ff12fa2bbce6136cf28f409496dd","tid":1550534,"uid":257620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T20:39:31.000Z","msg":"要 make a sample 下, <br />\n<br />\n打<br />\n<br />\n爆<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢<br />\n<br />\n地<br />\n<br />\n個<br />\n<br />\n頭<br />\n<br />\n等佢冇咁膠, 為佢地好"}]}